message.de_DE: Sehr erfreut über meine Anwesenheit scheinst du ja nicht gerade...
message.en_US: You don't really seem happy to see me.
message.ko_KR: 날 보게 된 걸 별로 반가워하지 않는군.

message.de_DE: Nette Aussicht von hier oben, oder?
message.en_US: Huh, nice view from here, don't you think?
message.zh_CN: 嗯，这儿的景观真不错，你觉得呢？

message.de_DE: ...Ahja, so toll ist sie auch nicht, schätze ich.

task.de_DE: Follow her! She is probably just shy!
task.en_US: Follow her! She is probably just shy!
task.zh_CN: 跟着她！她可能只是太害羞了！
task.ko_KR: 그녀를 쫓아가! 그저 부끄러워서 그런 것뿐일 거야!

message.de_DE: Macht es Spaß im Kreis zu laufen?
message.en_US: Do you have fun running in circles?

message.de_DE: Es sieht ja schon spaßig aus...

message.en_US: ... Do you mind if I... join you?
message.zh_CN: …如果你不介意的话…我可以加入吗？

message.de_DE: ...Hey, das verletzt mich jetzt schon so langsam, weißt du?
message.en_US: ...Hey, you really start hurting my feelings here!
message.zh_CN: …嘿！你这样真的有点伤我的心了！

task.de_DE: She probably just likes to stand on containers! Follow her!
task.en_US: She probably just likes to stand on containers! Follow her!
task.zh_CN: 她可能只是想站在箱子上罢了！跟着她！
task.ko_KR: 그녀는 그저 컨테이너에 의존하는 걸 좋아할 뿐일 거야! 그녀를 쫓아가!

message.en_US: Is there something wrong with me?
Why do you avoid me like that?

task.de_DE: She tries to escape! Quick! Follow her!
task.en_US: She tries to escape! Quick! Follow her!
task.ko_KR: 그녀가 도망치려고 하고 있어! 어서! 그녀를 쫓아가!

message.en_US: The path of a proper Spheromancer!

text.en_US: This is so mysterious, you guys!
